<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #374151;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .celebration-box {
        background: #d1fae5;
        border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .info-box {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .next-steps {
        background: #f0f9ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      }
      .next-steps ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .next-steps li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations!</h1>
      <p>Your organization is now fully activated</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="celebration-box">
        <h2>ðŸŽŠ Activation Complete!</h2>
        <p><strong><%= @organization.name %></strong> has been successfully activated and is ready to use!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Organization Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= @organization.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Tier:</strong> <%= @organization.tier.humanize %></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @organization.activation_status.humanize %></p>
        <p><strong>Activated:</strong> <%= @organization.updated_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
      </div>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3>What's Next?</h3>
        <p>Your organization is now fully operational. You can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access all organization features and settings</li>
          <li>Invite team members to your organization</li>
          <li>Configure additional settings and preferences</li>
          <li>Start using the full range of services</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Ready to get started? Access your organization dashboard:</p>
      
      <a href="<%= tenant_root_path %>" class="button">Go to Organization Dashboard</a>
      
      <p>Thank you for choosing HBS Data Processing! If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from HBS Data Processing System.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
